to get into it. It's very painful,
having to leave somebody.

23:04.280 --> 23:08.279
Just be thankful
that you're too young to know.

23:10.000 --> 23:13.999
Right, I think
I'd better ring a plumber.

23:18.800 --> 23:21.519
