your wedding photos, Frank.

23:44.160 --> 23:48.159
Cos what I've heard off Kev,
she'd be very interested in those,
seeing she's still married to you.

23:48.840 --> 23:52.839
Yeah, yeah, all right,
just get us another pint
and a couple of these, Jez.

23:59.360 --> 24:02.959
This had better be
a quick one before shopping.

24:02.960 --> 24:04.599
