25:40.520 --> 25:44.519
He'll be in soon enough. We'll just
have to wait here, won't we, Katie?

25:45.320 --> 25:46.519
What are you having?

25:46.520 --> 25:49.839
Erm, I'll have a juice. Pineapple.

25:49.840 --> 25:51.319
With vodka in it, thanks.

25:51.320 --> 25:51.719
Double?

25:51.720 --> 25:55.719
Yeah, why not?

26:00.080 --> 26:03.159
Ooh, look at you!

26:03.160 --> 26:04.599
It's nice.

26:04.600 --> 26:07.279
Yeah. But we need to talk.

26:07.280 --> 26:10.279
What's all this about, eh?

26:10.280 --> 26:14.279
