a bank, there's no way
we can afford this.

26:14.480 --> 26:17.919
No, you're right, we can't.

26:17.920 --> 26:21.919
It's always been my fantasy
to shag a man in a suit.

26:23.080 --> 26:25.039
Happy birthday!

26:25.040 --> 26:29.039
Thanks.

26:29.960 --> 26:33.959
BABY CRYING

26:35.760 --> 26:37.559
Sue! Sue!

26:37.560 --> 26:40.279
Can you fuck off
downstairs for an hour?

26:40.280 --> 26:42.079
