33:47.260 --> 33:51.259
Right, now get your bag,
you daft bint and hurry home.

33:51.940 --> 33:55.939
I'm not coming home, Norma.

33:55.940 --> 33:58.539
I'm staying with me family.

33:58.540 --> 33:59.819
What?

33:59.820 --> 34:03.819
I meant it.
God's spoken to me, sort of.

34:04.220 --> 34:06.099
I've had an epiphany.

34:06.100 --> 34:07.179
Ugh!

34:07.180 --> 34:10.539
Ugh!
No, Norma, don't listen!
She'll get you whatever you want.

34:10.540 --> 34:11.819
Won't you, Norma?

34:11.820 --> 34:15.819
You can't stay here anyway! It's too
cramped and we don't want you here!

34:16.300 --> 34:20.018
Oh, that's right! Hate me!

34:20.020 --> 34:22.779
Punish me forever
for one fucking mistake!

34:22.780 --> 34:26.779
I'm such a bad mother, aren't I?!
Such a bad fucking person!

34:27.219 --> 34:29.099
Hey. It's all right. Calm down.

34:29.100 --> 34:31.539
How can I, when she hates me!

34:31.540 --> 34:34.899
And she runs circles round
me, so I can't think straight.

34:34.900 --> 34:36.779
She doesn't hate you, Mum.

34:36.780 --> 34:38.179
None of us do.

34:38.179 --> 34:40.619
I don't understand
what this is about?!

34:40.620 --> 34:43.619
