36:15.500 --> 36:17.739
No, Stan!

36:17.740 --> 36:21.739
Sorry, PC Waterman.
Not without a warrant.

36:21.900 --> 36:24.499
Stay here. I'm going to get one.

36:24.500 --> 36:28.499
Off the premises, if you don't mind.

36:34.540 --> 36:37.539
